Actually it is not as obvious as I thought. Have you found the LOOKAT command? Somewhere in the middle is this:
```
  if (LengthOf(lookdesc) = 0) {
    lookdesc = Template("DefaultObjectDescription")
  }
```
Change it to:
```
  if (LengthOf(lookdesc) = 0) {
    lookdesc = "Nothing out of the ordinary"
  }
